      "text": "There will be a White House Press Briefing tomorrow. In the briefing room will be Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent & SBA Administrator Kelly Loeffler. A Senior Administration Official says it will be the continuation of highlighting tax day and the changes to the tax code in the One Big Beautiful Bill Act.\nThe Senior Admin Official says the highlights started with the McDonalds delivery Monday to the Oval Office by Doordash Grandma. \nThe Senior Admin Official says it continues with the briefing Wednesday and then finishes the week with President Trump highlighting no tax on tips in Las Vegas. #WhiteHouse",
